  <h2>Salzhemmendorf</h2>
  <p>Salzhemmendorf is a rural municipality with high quality of life, diverse nature, traditional customs and an active community. Approximately <strong>10,000 residents</strong> live in <strong>11 villages</strong>.</p>
  <h3>Highlights</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Ith-Sole Spa</strong> – Wellness and bathing fun</li>
    <li><strong>Rasti-Land</strong> – Theme park for the whole family</li>
    <li><strong>Historic Town Centre</strong> – Half-timbered houses and salt history</li>
    <li><strong>IthPunkt</strong> – Tourist information centre</li>
  </ul>
